{"tid":1870932,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"［行動post無人推?］知道大家好緊張口罩，但抗爭係咪完左？","createTime":"2020-02-09T07:15:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-10T02:19:04.000Z","uid":42194,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"e32997dd2fe8b648798eb6332e3cd51935bf72c3","tid":1870932,"uid":42194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T07:15:30.000Z","msg":"明白大家好緊張口罩同疫情，呢個絕對明白嘅<br />\n但係咪代表大家可以訓覺同埋叫2盒thx就ok了？<br />\n<br />\n尋晚將軍澳好多手足出左黎，正正係同大家講，抗爭未完架！<br />\n<br />\n響呢個日子裡面，好似無乜活動可以參與？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">當然唔係！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n民間集會團隊今晚會作個新嘗試<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Cyber集會</span>]</span><br />\n<br />\n今晚可以一齊YouTube 見嗎？即使好似好鳩好冷氣，大家可以一齊推post, 一齊嘗試下做返次先？<br />\n大家今晚一齊用最簡單嘅方式睇個live, 去表示抗爭未完，仲有好多同路人架，可以嗎？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/krT1iSC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkrT1iSC.jpg&h=5b55ab7b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SSLyUqZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSSLyUqZ.jpg&h=7691e2b2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PFeDk50.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPFeDk50.jpg&h=71d16921&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n時代抗疫 &bull; 全民連線集氣夜<br />\n跨媒體集氣平台<br />\n<br />\n日期：2020年2月9日 (日)<br />\n時間：19:00-21:00<br />\n直播：民間集會團隊YouTube Channel<br />\nLink：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/HKCATLive\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2FHKCATLive&d=CEXeqV9R6719hdRRqmVjOrTr7UizNwCuyTydxCoZ6r4%3D&h=024aff2d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/HKCATLive</a><br />\n========================<br />\n疫症襲港，抗爭不息。<br />\n<br />\n民間集會團隊繼續同香港人齊上齊落，做返我哋擅長嘅事：搞集會！<br />\n<br />\n今次轉以網上形式，請各位同我哋一齊，防疫不忘抗爭。<br />\n<br />\n民集希望感謝落力抗疫嘅每一個你，今次接受市民事先報名phone-in，名額有限，每位有約十分鐘發言時間。<br />\n<br />\n第一節<br />\n【政府無能 前線受災 醫護撐住！】<br />\n🔸感激醫護罷工救港，由沙士到武漢肺炎堅守專業，不論前線醫護、家屬、病人定普通公眾，打嚟一齊集氣撐住！<br />\n<br />\n第二節<br />\n【防疫兒戲 全民受害 港人反抗！】<br />\n🔸政府遲遲唔全面封關，強制隔離措施兒戲可笑。<br />\n🔸各行各業點樣受疫症威脅？香港人要做啲咩自救？集會平台俾你講！<br />\n<br />\n有意報名發言請dm @hkcat_contact<br />\n提供以下資料：<br />\n- 稱呼<br />\n- 行業/身份<br />\n- 發言內容概要 (十分鐘內)<br />\n<br />\n專人會聯絡閣下，通知報名結果，成功者會安排發言時間。<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n支持民間集會團隊（眾籌/參與）：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/s/HKCATeam\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fs%2FHKCATeam&d=CEXeqV9R6719hdRRqmVjOrTr7UizNwCuyTydxCoZ6r4%3D&h=27c8cbc1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/s/HKCATeam</a><br />\n參與/洽詢合作：<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/HKCATeam_bot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FHKCATeam_bot&d=CEXeqV9R6719hdRRqmVjOrTr7UizNwCuyTydxCoZ6r4%3D&h=7f4355e0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/HKCATeam_bot</a><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n我們的最新動向/合作洽詢：<br />\nFacebook：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HKCATeam/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHKCATeam%2F&d=CEXeqV9R6719hdRRqmVjOrTr7UizNwCuyTydxCoZ6r4%3D&h=79cc3d8d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HKCATeam/</a><br />\nInstagram：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/HKCAT/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2FHKCAT%2F&d=CEXeqV9R6719hdRRqmVjOrTr7UizNwCuyTydxCoZ6r4%3D&h=ab851a82\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/HKCAT/</a><br />\nTwitter：<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/HKCATeam\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FHKCATeam&d=CEXeqV9R6719hdRRqmVjOrTr7UizNwCuyTydxCoZ6r4%3D&h=1ae25ad9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/HKCATeam</a><br />\n<br />\n亦請大家推埋呢個post<br />\n<br />\n[新行動] 時代抗疫。全民連線集氣<br />\n夜 - 唔該推上熱門<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1869942\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1869942</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命"},{"pid":"efddb31aecfaaaafd3a57c971e6b93bdd1e4a213","tid":1870932,"uid":42194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T07:15:48.000Z","msg":"推1"},{"pid":"2985e421b1181d25ece435ae8a2443ea86f3ec39","tid":1870932,"uid":59297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T07:15:52.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"5de6509f8dcf10cc520b329c7e19a8f7aa8d79fd","tid":1870932,"uid":42194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T07:16:01.000Z","msg":"推2"},{"pid":"779f613c59cc6b2fa6b789b951d2fe4574b02d67","tid":1870932,"uid":59297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T07:16:03.000Z","msg":"行動"},{"pid":"069cef38a6421eb0f5a86aef9b88162921f28c55","tid":1870932,"uid":345458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T07:16:04.000Z","msg":"柒野梗係要攞返出嚟推<br />\n<br />\n各位巴打入一入黎<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1783569\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1783569</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d9a3f9dc8d70527eabf62de8d46f441942677629","tid":1870932,"uid":42194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T07:16:16.000Z","msg":"推3"},{"pid":"33de8237bf8140bab600680ff23d5afcdaf17778","tid":1870932,"uid":42194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T07:17:49.000Z","msg":"推4"},{"pid":"e420ec5d3e2a52f88d8621dc8e086d48e9c020ca","tid":1870932,"uid":42194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T07:17:59.000Z","msg":"推5"},{"pid":"dcd8b8edcdf3781ce6347e0b2509827151e92bfa","tid":1870932,"uid":42194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T07:18:09.000Z","msg":"推6"},{"pid":"3ce9fee1d84e5910a2ba0beb69591efb93072eea","tid":1870932,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"